  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/48b0de50e18f70722cfe42e79edbd3cd.poster.avif?t=1711569728\" width=566 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/48b0de50e18f70722cfe42e79edbd3cd.webm?t=1711569728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/48b0de50e18f70722cfe42e79edbd3cd.mp4?t=1711569728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Features<br>Deceptively simple controls:  Almost every interaction in the game is handled with a simple swipe left or right.<br><br>Engaging story:  Adventure with a colorful cast of characters that accompany you on your adventures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/f6656c7e2e10420c21fd037467e30526.poster.avif?t=1711569728\" width=566 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/f6656c7e2e10420c21fd037467e30526.webm?t=1711569728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/f6656c7e2e10420c21fd037467e30526.mp4?t=1711569728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rich depth of builds and combos:  Choosing cards to add to your deck will be critical in surviving your adventures.  With over 1000 cards, the combinations are endless.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570830/extras/50b98ec1b6a0d0ba3541189624caa9a5.poster.avif?t=1711569728\" width=566 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto